174 A.3d 513 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. SHARIF O. LEE, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-195 September Term 2017

079422 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004399-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
